# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Backend Framework & Language
- **Language**: Java 21 (LTS)
- **Framework**: Spring Boot 3.x
- **Build Tool**: Gradle (Kotlin DSL or Groovy) or Maven (Default to Gradle if not specified)

## Database & Storage
- **RDBMS**: MySQL 8.x (InnoDB Engine)
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
- **Storage**: Object Storage (AWS S3 or compatible) for PDF/Excel evidence

## Document Generation (Microservice)
- **Language**: Python
- **Framework**: FastAPI
- **Libraries**: LangChain (for template/LLM integration)

## AI & External
- **LLM Provider**: OpenAI API or Google Gemini (via Gateway)
- **Integration**: LangChain (Python layer)

## Communication
- **API Style**: REST (JSON)
- **Documentation**: Swagger / OpenAPI 3.0
- **Messaging**: KakaoTalk / SMS Gateway integration

